descriptionHtml:
Our proposed solution uses technology for better learning outcomes and personalized learning system for engineering mathematics education. With the help of Artificial intelligence to create the adaptive learning solution for engineering mathematics education to transform teacher centered to learner centered education.
● Proposed solution is Exclusive Content Platform Solution for Engineering
Mathematics, with customized university.
● The Web & App based platform has inbuilt LMS which can be used by Professors for effective teaching, assessments and tracking students progress.
● Students can use this platform as a self learning tool
● Even the tough mathematics concepts can be explained in an easier understanding way with our step by step animated video.

Why Maths.Engineering Works
● One Platform for all Engineering Mathematics chapters.
● Clear up Tough Topics: Learn a complex problem in 10 minutes without guidance, Let check in demo.
● Short & Self-explanatory solution – A 40 mins board solving problem is solved in less than 10 mins without missing any steps.
● Make Progress Quickly: With our Step by Step animated problem solving video's you'll be able to make a quick learning progress in all Math papers.
● Curated Content: 200 + solved self-explanatory animated videos in each subject, topic wise prioritize solved problems.
● Personalized Learning: Customized content tailored to your university curriculum and learning it in your language will help you to learn at the right level and pace.
● Learn Your Way: Anytime, Anywhere in your Languages.
● Can be used both by Students & Faculties.
● Vernacular- English, Tamil, Telugu, Hindi and many more languages to come.
● Solved Question Papers
● Reviewed & Verified by Experienced Math's Faculties

Major elements of proposed Adaptive learning
● 1. Understanding the problem: self - explanatory step by step animated videos to explain simple, complex mathematics problems. We have worked out minutes 5 problems for each chapter to ensure we cover every method in the chapter.
● 2. Practice problem: Related topic problems for practice, provided answers and hints to solve.

descriptionHtml:
The Maths.Engineering platform is a digital guide that covers all topics that are relevant to engineering mathematics. The platform functions both as an instructional tool for faculties and as a self-learning tool for students.

Our digital platform is the first of its kind, to use immersive videos of solved problems to help learners easily understand the mathematics concepts. Every video will have step-by-step animations along with quick tips which will help learners to excel will in their examinations.

Our Platform covers many of the leading Technical (State, Deemed, Private) university syllabus Patterns. We’re constantly adding more mathematics topics to ensure we cover all Engineering Mathematics topics at a global level.

Freemium Model
This is a Freemium Model platform where learners are given options to view a set of solved problems videos at no cost. If learners wish to access the complete course they can upgrade to the premium model by paying nominal subscription fees.

• Engaging, animated tutorials that make learning complex concepts simple and fun.

• Bite-sized videos for quick learning and easy revision, perfect for the busy student.
• A comprehensive library of important semester questions, with proven success in past exams.

EMPOWER YOUR LEARNING WITH:
• Immediate access to crucial exam prep resources and essential semester questions.
• The convenience of learning anywhere, anytime.
• A user-friendly mobile app designed for efficient, on-the-go learning experiences.
• Our track record of success: Students who used our essential questions aced their exams.

ACHIEVE YOUR GOALS WITH MATHS.ENGINEERING:
• Build confidence and mastery in your college math courses.
